Title: Moving out
Paragraphs:
Last month, TODAYonline published a piece by one of its journalists that described her experience moving out as a single woman. The article drew in thousands of comments online, with many netizens slamming the 32 year old for her move.

This got us wondering – are Singaporeans ready for a culture of leaving the nest before/without getting married?
Author: Faizal Kamal
